```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant ADO as Azure DevOps
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant ORC as Orchestrator
    participant DEV as Dev Agent
    participant TEST as Test Agent
    participant NEON as Neon
    participant REDIS as Redis

    ADO->>GW: Service Hook (Draft PR Trigger)
    GW->>ORC: Task Dispatch (Redis Stream entry)
    ORC->>NEON: Fetch Context
    ORC->>DEV: Execute Task (Draft PR)
    DEV->>ADO: Create Branch & Draft PR
    ORC->>TEST: Run Tests
    TEST->>ADO: Update Checks
    ORC->>NEON: Persist Result
    ORC->>REDIS: Update Queue State
    ORC->>GW: Completion Event
    GW->>ADO: Status (Comment / Check)
```
